content: I think I'm going to start with purging and decluttering. I need to get rid of all the expired products and items I no longer use. It'll be a good opportunity to go through everything and see what I can donate or throw away. Then, I can start thinking about how I want to organize what's left. I've been trying to stick to a daily cleaning routine for a while now, and this is just another part of that process. It's all about creating good habits and making my life easier in the long run.
